            . I work at Mr. Evans', the stove-makers. On Sunday evening, the 14th of June, between seven and eight o'clock, I was on <placeName id="t18290611-356-crimeloc1867">Londonbridge</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18290611-356-crimeloc1867" type="placeName" value="Londonbridge"></interp>
